a great place to start one thing i love about greatest hits packages from groups with only one legitimate hit is that you never grow tired of them . timbuk 3 's greatest hits package is a good place to start enjoying their music and you will not get tired of hearing songs you 've heard a million times on the radio . if you want more info on the band seach the web because there is a least one great web site . after buying this cd and the live one you will have to seach the used bins and i highly recommend the album eden alley